{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-component-tsx","path":"/component/Modal/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"359e9ef0-aea6-5e0d-a3f6-b3413558b402","excerpt":"简介 弹窗  一种临时窗口，是打断用户当前操作流程，获取用户视觉焦点的对话框。 常用于提供反馈信息、确认操作行为等场景，也可用于承载简单的表单信息填写、表格信息展示等，使用户在不离开当前页面的情况下，能够快速执行简单的操作。 弹窗  通常会出现在屏幕的中间位置，会对界面的主要内容造成遮挡。 基本构成  标题（A…","html":"<!--副标题具体写法见源代码模式-->\n<h2 id=\"简介\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\" aria-label=\"简介 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>简介</h2>\n<p>弹窗 <code class=\"language-text\">Modal</code> 一种临时窗口，是打断用户当前操作流程，获取用户视觉焦点的对话框。</p>\n<p>常用于提供反馈信息、确认操作行为等场景，也可用于承载简单的表单信息填写、表格信息展示等，使用户在不离开当前页面的情况下，能够快速执行简单的操作。</p>\n<p>弹窗 <code class=\"language-text\">Modal</code> 通常会出现在屏幕的中间位置，会对界面的主要内容造成遮挡。</p>\n<h2 id=\"基本构成\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90\" aria-label=\"基本构成 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本构成</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"forms 01\"\n        title=\"forms 01\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/42cb2c51d1b3f91487fbaaa82e3924b1/dc3b8/forms_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/42cb2c51d1b3f91487fbaaa82e3924b1/8ef26/forms_01.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/42cb2c51d1b3f91487fbaaa82e3924b1/c4481/forms_01.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/42cb2c51d1b3f91487fbaaa82e3924b1/dc3b8/forms_01.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/42cb2c51d1b3f91487fbaaa82e3924b1/5620d/forms_01.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">标题（A）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">关闭按钮（B）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">内容区域（C）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">底部操作区域（D）</th>\n<th align=\"center\">提示信息（E）</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可选</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">√</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可选</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"基本样式\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"基本样式 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本样式</h2>\n<h3 id=\"尺寸\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8\" aria-label=\"尺寸 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>尺寸</h3>\n<p>弹窗 <code class=\"language-text\">Modal</code> 预设了 <code class=\"language-text\">sm</code>、<code class=\"language-text\">md</code>、<code class=\"language-text\">lg</code>三种尺寸，宽度分别为400px、700px、800px。</p>\n<p><strong>小号弹窗</strong></p>\n<p>主要用于重要级比较高的信息提示，是一种强提醒，可以确保用户知晓，常用于重要操作后结果的展示，或危险、警告等信息的展示。</p>\n<p>如果仅用于反馈操作结果的状态信息，不希望干扰用户的操作流时，建议使用 <a href=\"https://udesign.ucloud.cn/component/Message/\">Message 全局提示</a> 组件。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 790px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sm\"\n        title=\"sm\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/58c263008c69aa8558c89eca0fd84d9d/71c01/sm.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/58c263008c69aa8558c89eca0fd84d9d/8ef26/sm.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/58c263008c69aa8558c89eca0fd84d9d/c4481/sm.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/58c263008c69aa8558c89eca0fd84d9d/71c01/sm.png 790w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 790px) 100vw, 790px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>中号弹窗</strong>\n中号弹窗是最常使用的尺寸。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1366px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.388888888888886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"md\"\n        title=\"md\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/b5cdee27a02c0276f042ce9cea3e3ee1/201ce/md.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/b5cdee27a02c0276f042ce9cea3e3ee1/8ef26/md.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/b5cdee27a02c0276f042ce9cea3e3ee1/c4481/md.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/b5cdee27a02c0276f042ce9cea3e3ee1/201ce/md.png 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>大号弹窗</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.22222222222223%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lg\"\n        title=\"lg\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/2c2837eedad283cd37aaab436ffd2e75/dc3b8/lg.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/2c2837eedad283cd37aaab436ffd2e75/8ef26/lg.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/2c2837eedad283cd37aaab436ffd2e75/c4481/lg.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/2c2837eedad283cd37aaab436ffd2e75/dc3b8/lg.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/2c2837eedad283cd37aaab436ffd2e75/9bf4a/lg.png 1566w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"弹窗高度\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BC%B9%E7%AA%97%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6\" aria-label=\"弹窗高度 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>弹窗高度</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>内容区域未限定最大高度：弹窗高度根据内容区域高度自适应；</li>\n<li>内容区域设置了最大高度：内容区域出现滚动条，其他构成不随内容区域滚动。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1352px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 88.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"height\"\n        title=\"height\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/735ff5d1d35065a89eec9d7de5d68679/53d80/height.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/735ff5d1d35065a89eec9d7de5d68679/8ef26/height.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/735ff5d1d35065a89eec9d7de5d68679/c4481/height.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/735ff5d1d35065a89eec9d7de5d68679/53d80/height.png 1352w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1352px) 100vw, 1352px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"默认提示\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"默认提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>默认提示</h3>\n<p>弹窗的默认提示与弹窗等宽，位于内容卡片与弹窗标题之间，具体设置，可以参考<a href=\"https://udesign.ucloud.cn/component/Notice/\">Notice 提示</a>。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 618px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 138.05555555555554%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"defaultnotice\"\n        title=\"defaultnotice\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/ab67ac35a0d7c2b145f988f03902e8f5/8e854/defaultnotice.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/ab67ac35a0d7c2b145f988f03902e8f5/8ef26/defaultnotice.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/ab67ac35a0d7c2b145f988f03902e8f5/8e854/defaultnotice.png 618w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 618px) 100vw, 618px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"报错提示\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA\" aria-label=\"报错提示 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>报错提示</h3>\n<p>弹窗全局的报错，在内容区顶部进行报错。内容区域内表单/表格的报错，遵循 <a href=\"https://udesign.ucloud.cn/component/Form/\">Form 表单</a> 和 <a href=\"https://udesign.ucloud.cn/component/Table/\">Table 表格</a> 的报错原则。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.83333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"errornotice\"\n        title=\"errornotice\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/9d5362b0ce9b4ddfc46f3d9f20096ef5/dc3b8/errornotice.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/9d5362b0ce9b4ddfc46f3d9f20096ef5/8ef26/errornotice.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/9d5362b0ce9b4ddfc46f3d9f20096ef5/c4481/errornotice.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/9d5362b0ce9b4ddfc46f3d9f20096ef5/dc3b8/errornotice.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/9d5362b0ce9b4ddfc46f3d9f20096ef5/c4c55/errornotice.png 1524w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"异步加载\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E5%8A%A0%E8%BD%BD\" aria-label=\"异步加载 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>异步加载</h3>\n<p>适用于当前操作需要异步完成，等待后再自动关闭对话框。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1102px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"loading\"\n        title=\"loading\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/958fb71468d565d92265589af767c9e3/bc10f/loading.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/958fb71468d565d92265589af767c9e3/8ef26/loading.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/958fb71468d565d92265589af767c9e3/c4481/loading.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/958fb71468d565d92265589af767c9e3/bc10f/loading.png 1102w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1102px) 100vw, 1102px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"设计说明\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-label=\"设计说明 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设计说明</h2>\n<h3 id=\"弹窗标题\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BC%B9%E7%AA%97%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"弹窗标题 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>弹窗标题</h3>\n<p>若弹窗是由用户主动触发的，那么弹窗标题应该与用户触发弹窗的操作按钮同名，或者至少有相同的关键字。此时弹窗是用户操作后的反馈，用户需要通过弹窗的标题来确认自己是否进入了正确的模块、进行了正确的操作。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"title\"\n        title=\"title\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/896d9619d33576ab09a88bba64fb85b1/dc3b8/title.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/896d9619d33576ab09a88bba64fb85b1/8ef26/title.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/896d9619d33576ab09a88bba64fb85b1/c4481/title.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/896d9619d33576ab09a88bba64fb85b1/dc3b8/title.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/896d9619d33576ab09a88bba64fb85b1/62fcd/title.png 2044w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>如果弹窗是系统主动弹出的，弹窗标题简单陈述问题、询问行为或者作出行为建议。内容区的说明文字展开来解释出现问题的原因，以及操作后的后果。避免使用无效标题。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 704px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"title 2\"\n        title=\"title 2\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/0464264877b4af89bb001e120fd584de/b1838/title-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/0464264877b4af89bb001e120fd584de/8ef26/title-2.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/0464264877b4af89bb001e120fd584de/b1838/title-2.png 704w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 704px) 100vw, 704px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"弹窗的关闭方式\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BC%B9%E7%AA%97%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"弹窗的关闭方式 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>弹窗的关闭方式</h3>\n<p>弹窗 <code class=\"language-text\">Modal</code> 作为一个非常底层的控件，应该兼顾大部分用户的不同习惯，从而保持整个系统有比较好的可用性。因此，U-Design建议在弹窗的右上角添加“x”作为关闭操作性弹窗的最短路径，并且佐以键控、点击遮罩等多种关闭方式；除非要求用户明确表态（比如要求同意协议）的情况，可以只通过操作按钮关闭。</p>\n<p>当然，更便捷的关闭方式代表着更多的误触，如何平衡可用性和误触，就要根据具体场景具体分析。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.83333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"close\"\n        title=\"close\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/5cf8c56f003c07c6d5e2e1dbca751010/dc3b8/close.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/5cf8c56f003c07c6d5e2e1dbca751010/8ef26/close.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/5cf8c56f003c07c6d5e2e1dbca751010/c4481/close.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/5cf8c56f003c07c6d5e2e1dbca751010/dc3b8/close.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/5cf8c56f003c07c6d5e2e1dbca751010/23a93/close.png 1632w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"5模态与非模态\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5%E6%A8%A1%E6%80%81%E4%B8%8E%E9%9D%9E%E6%A8%A1%E6%80%81\" aria-label=\"5模态与非模态 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5.模态与非模态</h3>\n<p>弹窗分为模态与非模态两种，支持自定义\n模态：可自定义是否可以通过蒙层关闭弹窗。\n非模态：可拖拽</p>\n<h2 id=\"常见问题\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"常见问题 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>常见问题</h2>\n<h3 id=\"模态对话框与抽屉使用时的区别\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%A8%A1%E6%80%81%E5%AF%B9%E8%AF%9D%E6%A1%86%E4%B8%8E%E6%8A%BD%E5%B1%89%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\" aria-label=\"模态对话框与抽屉使用时的区别 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>模态对话框与抽屉使用时的区别</h3>\n<div class=\"u-md-flex-without-bg\">\n   <div class=\"u-md-mr24\">\n      <p><i class=\"u-md-suggested\"></i>当内容较少时使用弹窗展示，当内容较多时使用抽屉展示。</p>\n      <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image alt\" title=\"desc\" src=\"/u-design/static/92defde41643c4e2152985f5120b4941/c6e50/problems_01.png\" srcset=\"/u-design/static/92defde41643c4e2152985f5120b4941/8ef26/problems_01.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/92defde41643c4e2152985f5120b4941/c4481/problems_01.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/92defde41643c4e2152985f5120b4941/c6e50/problems_01.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">desc</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n   </div>\n   <div>\n      <p><i class=\"u-md-not-suggested\"></i>当内容较多时，弹窗内会出现滚动条，不便于用户使用。</p>\n      <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1000px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image alt\" title=\"desc\" src=\"/u-design/static/724739c5dc082b260010eecd3dc71185/c6e50/problems_02.png\" srcset=\"/u-design/static/724739c5dc082b260010eecd3dc71185/8ef26/problems_02.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/724739c5dc082b260010eecd3dc71185/c4481/problems_02.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/724739c5dc082b260010eecd3dc71185/c6e50/problems_02.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">desc</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n   </div>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"相关文档\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3\" aria-label=\"相关文档 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>相关文档</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/u-design/component/Button/\">Button 按钮</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/u-design/component/Form/\">Form 表单</a></li>\n</ol>","headings":[{"value":"简介","depth":2},{"value":"基本构成","depth":2},{"value":"基本样式","depth":2},{"value":"尺寸","depth":3},{"value":"弹窗高度","depth":3},{"value":"默认提示","depth":3},{"value":"报错提示","depth":3},{"value":"异步加载","depth":3},{"value":"设计说明","depth":2},{"value":"弹窗标题","depth":3},{"value":"弹窗的关闭方式","depth":3},{"value":"5.模态与非模态","depth":3},{"value":"常见问题","depth":2},{"value":"模态对话框与抽屉使用时的区别","depth":3},{"value":"相关文档","depth":2}],"fields":{"slug":"/component/list/Modal/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":"打断用户的当前操作流程，获取用户视觉焦点的对话框。","order":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"359e9ef0-aea6-5e0d-a3f6-b3413558b402"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3000541721","850322689"]}